# Animation Rules (motion.dev)

## Principles

- Animations must be subtle and purposeful
- Avoid excessive motion
- Prioritize performance

## Usage

- Use motion.dev for all animations
- Prefer declarative animations
- Use variants for reusable animation patterns

## Patterns

- Fade-in + slight translate for sections
- Stagger animations for lists
- Hover animations for interactivity

## Performance

- Avoid heavy animations on large lists
- Use GPU-friendly properties (transform, opacity)

## UX

- Animations should enhance, not distract
- Keep durations between 0.2s – 0.6s